{"tid":1502241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叫人「唔好」我當你係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:44:56.000Z","uid":292536,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05ffdcd4cd77e4204fda0a428012fa228e5363c5","tid":1502241,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=414348935875795&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D414348935875795%26_rdr&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84mhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=775eec3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=414348935875795&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n每逢有以眼還眼嘅機會出現，我方總係會有個耶穌嘅化身出現，釋出無比嘅愛叫人收手叫人停。以上嘅片段中可以聽到某人不停講「唔好唔好」。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位前線可唔可以下次即刻當呢啲係鬼咁處理</span></strong>，因為咁樣拖後腿一係就今次咁無啦啦錯失千載難逢嘅機會，唔係就85咁76位手足畀人送死。不分化、不割蓆、不篤魁嘅原則係建基於互相冇影響嘅情況之下，咁樣阻撓法明顯唔再係兄弟爬山，唔好用呢個藉口做擋箭牌。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望各位可以將和事佬一律當鬼處理。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n講完。"},{"pid":"681b81bc4ff63519a7715aaf50066a5116f3a41c","tid":1502241,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6d5efbd84d94e455c43f0c2c3f2f0a4357029b15","tid":1502241,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:30:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾左膠無處不在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64204a78f340d9e054b05aa32e1d791b54b1761f","tid":1502241,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"各位幫手推下，我唔想見到左膠喺到累人累物"},{"pid":"ebcf368b93de0ca9aa8d338582e54c20e270a0d1","tid":1502241,"uid":151304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0